00:00:00.512 --> 00:00:02.304
<b>An end-range wrist motion</b>

00:00:02.560 --> 00:00:04.608
<b>plus a powerful or fast push</b>

00:00:04.864 --> 00:00:08.704
<b>can result in extreme force on the tendons and nerves of your wrist.</b>

00:00:09.472 --> 00:00:12.120
<b>Learning to push with the little finger side of the palm</b>

00:00:12.288 --> 00:00:14.956
<b>reduces strain because the force is directed</b>

00:00:15.104 --> 00:00:18.248
<b>to stronger tendons and muscles along the side of the wrist.</b>

